7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Canva AI and Hotpot AI share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Image, Inpainting, Upscaling, Commercial License. Where Canva AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Outpainting and Style Transfer, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Hotpot AI uniquely offers Image To Image and Api Access, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Canva AI holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 10/10, while Hotpot AI scores 5/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Canva AI and Hotpot AI offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Canva AI's free tier and Hotpot AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
